data.description: This is an extremely well built 3-bedroom, 2 bathrooms and a 2-car garage home.  It is located on a cul de sac in North Pole, very close to schools, shopping plus it’s only 15 minutes to Fairbanks/Ft Wainwright and Eielson Air Force Base.  The open floor plan and 9-foot ceilings gives a much larger feel.  The radiant floor heat and efficient Buderus boiler cuts down on heating cost while keeping you nice and cozy.  In the master suite you will enjoy the dual solid surface vanity top, walk-in shower and walk-in closet.  The established lawn and recycled asphalt (RAP) driveway make this home look amazing the moment you drive up.  It is also on city utilities so no bad water or a failed septic system to worry about.  The perfect move ready home awaits your arrival.
